      <h1>Sermon Publisher</h1>
      <p>
        The Covid-19 pandemic is forcing churches to find new ways to engage
        with their members. Sermon publisher allows pastors to publish sermons
        to the Internet from their mobile phones. It has two components: A
        mobile app for the pastor to publish sermons. And a public website for
        people to listen to the sermons.
      </p>

      <h2>Pastor App</h2>
      <p>
        The pastor app has a login screen, a list of sermons and a form for
        uploading new sermons. Pastors notify their audience that a new sermon
        is available by sharing the link via WhatsApp, SMS, Email etc.
      </p>
